  "description": "<p>Compatibility fork of PopOut! for Foundry V14 users whose systems still use legacy Application V1 sheets that do not receive Foundry's native ApplicationV2 pop-out button.</p><p>Adds a PopOut! button to most actor sheets, item sheets, journal entries, and applications so they can be opened in a separate browser window.</p>",
